OL,6,FThe club went further on and called on
OL,7,FPGMOL to change its rules on
OL,8,Fofficials' allegiances to account for
OL,9,F"contextual rivalries in the league
OL,10,Ftable", not just local rivalries.
OL,12,FThe Premier League said it was
OL,13,F"extremely disappointed" by the
OL,14,Fstatement issued on Sunday and added:
OL,15,F"It is never appropriate to improperly
OL,16,Fquestion the integrity of match
OL,17,Fofficials, and the nature of these
OL,18,Fcomments means the Premier League will
OL,19,Falso be investigating the matter in
OL,20,Frelation to the league's rules."
