OL,4,Cnext season after Wolves forces vote
OL,6,FWell, after Wolves request, a Premier
OL,7,FLeague spokesperson said: "The Premier
OL,8,FLeague can confirm it will facilitate
OL,9,Fa discussion on VAR with our clubs at
OL,10,Fthe Annual General Meeting next month.
OL,12,F"Clubs are entitled to put forward
OL,13,Fproposals at Shareholders' meetings
OL,14,Fand we acknowledge the concerns and
OL,15,Fissues around the use of VAR."
OL,17,F"However, the League fully supports
OL,18,Fthe use of VAR and remains committed,
OL,19,Falongside PGMOL, to make continued
OL,20,Fimprovements to the system for the
OL,21,Fbenefit of the game and fans."
